    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that will need to be addressed before it can be used reliably. The exterior shows considerable wear, including multiple scratches and dents. The interior is worn and has visible damage. This vehicle is best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or use it for parts.",
